        <h2>Aloevera</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Aloe vera is beneficial for your hair. The vitamins and minerals present in aloe vera help to detoxify the scalp, thereby helping you remove impurities. 
            Besides, it repairs the scalp, reduces dandruff, and promotes hair growth.
             In fact, aloe vera has nutrition-rich compounds that nourish your scalp and soften the texture of your hair.</p>
        <p>How to use</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Mix 2 tbsp aloe vera and 4-5 drops of tea tree oil together.</li>
            <li>Apply the mixture all over your scalp, and massage for 4-5 minutes.</li>
            <li>Now, leave it for 10-15 minutes and then wash it off. </li>
        </ol>
