        <h2>Lemon juice</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>lemon is the most effective home remedy for a greasy and oily scalp. The acidic nature of lemon helps to remove excess oil or sebum from your hair, and also works as a great solution for dandruff. 
            It also kills bacteria, and helps to keep the oil away from your scalp. </p>
        <p>How to use</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Grind a handful of mint leaves and mix them with 2 tbsp lemon juice and 1 tbsp yogurt.</li>
            <li>Apply it on your scalp and hair, and let the mixture sit for 15 minutes. Do massage your scalp with this mixture.</li>
            <li>Now, wash it off with cold water.</li>
        </ol>
