        <h2> Egg white pack</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Egg white is rich in protein and high in sulfur, which can help you tackle oily hair and dandruff. 
            Not to mention, it also helps in nourishing and conditioning your hair. </p>
        <p>How to use </p>
        <ol>
            <li> Break an egg and separate the yolk,2 tbsp honey, and mix it well with egg yolk.</li>
            <li>Let it sit for 10 minutes, before applying it to the scalp.</li>
            <li>Massage your hair with this mixture for five minutes, and then let it stay on for about 20 minutes.Rinse it off with normal water.</li>
